{"tid":387912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大仇口? 馬鞍山2的士8條胎全被插穿刑毀","createTime":"2017-09-05T04:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T18:36:24.000Z","uid":122,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"253f501772e38beb19927728b3220c6690d8f01c","tid":387912,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:41:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>咁大仇口? 馬鞍山2的士8條胎全被插穿刑毀</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170905/large/1504583811_1326.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170905%2Flarge%2F1504583811_1326.jpg&h=04faa293&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山富安花園對出的士站，泊有多部市區的士。早上9時許，有的士司機返回取車開工，發現其中2部市區的士共8條車胎全部被人用利器插穿，司機報警求助。警方正調查兇徒動機。<br />\n<br />\n肇事2部的士的司機返署協助調查。拖車師傅到場善後，其他的士行家亦前來幫手。現場所見，的士每條車胎被人用尖銳物件插穿2至3個洞，拖車師傅表示，兇徒以橫向的手法插穿車胎，令車胎無法修補，必須要換胎。<br />\n<br />\n其中一部的士的打理人表示，每部的士換胎連車租損失約3000多元。肇事的士昨晚由替更司機駕駛，他住在富安花園，遂將的士泊在附近，以往未試過在此處泊車。<br />\n<br />\n你敢爆，我敢獎！ 即Call《蘋果》24小時爆相爆片熱線：63836568"},{"pid":"c46deb46512adbe9c7988a1abbbd9eb88deeb3d7","tid":387912,"uid":810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:43:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4719cf55cd039fd219d1e75777a2425f0178842","tid":387912,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:44:51.000Z","msg":"以往未試過在此處泊車<br />\n陀地位？好易查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9e5f04e67f16d6f09621cff9360814f663b809d","tid":387912,"uid":17081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T04:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://blog.menclub.hk/hkfilmsnewreviews/wp-content/uploads/sites/164/2016/12/4740119957_b179f50188.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.menclub.hk%2Fhkfilmsnewreviews%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F164%2F2016%2F12%2F4740119957_b179f50188.jpg&h=c4525972&